high_descs: Turn around and walk to the front of the stove.
Grab the lettuce to the right of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and move to the front of the sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill the lettuce in the fridge and put it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and move forward, then turn left to face the counter between the sink and the stove.
Pick up the lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and go forward to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce inside of the fridge, then take it out.
Turn around and go forward to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink basin
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your right, take two steps, and turn left to face the counter to right of the stove
Pick up the cabbage from the counter
Turn back and go to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the cabbage inside the fridge, close the door, wait a few seconds, and take the cabbage out of the fridge
Turn left and again turn, go to the sink
Put the cabbage in the sink basin
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled cabbage in the sink
